<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV33">
<l>miṉṉiṟatte yiṟṟarakkaṉ vīḻaveñca ranturantu</l>
<l>piṉṉavaṟka ruḷpurinta racaḷitta peṟṟiyōy</l>
<l>naṉṉiṟatto riñcolēḻai piṉṉaikēḷva maṉṉucīr</l>
<l>poṉṉiṟatta vaṇṇaṉāya puṇṭarīka ṉallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O great [Lord] who shot a cruel arrow so that the Rakshasa</l>
<l rend="indent">with lightning-hued teeth fell,</l>
<l>blessed [his] younger brother, and gave [him] the kingdom!</l>
<l>O Husband of the simple Piṉṉai with a good complexion and sweet words!</l>
<l>Are you not the lotus[-eyed Lord] with enduring excellence and a golden hue?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
